To a story that is sending chills down the spine of residents of Nyeri County and it is emerging that five people have been abducted by unknown people in the last five days. Yesterday, a businessman Gerald Guandarua was abducted and his whereabouts remain unknown. Reports indicate that among the people who have been kidnapped are three family members and an employee to one of them. And as Daniel Kariuki reports, residents of Nyeri are now wondering who the identities of the abductors are?
